Uniquely innovative – our Creative Products
T’n’T®, Yellow Sub and Fantasia® –three extraordinary hop compositions
The specially balanced creations T’n’T®, Yellow Sub und Fantasia® – developed by BARTH-HAAS using top-secret formulas – allow you to brew interesting and sophisticated beers with a diverse range of intense flavours.
 




