Passion and expertise
		

for successful beers. 
		

More >




 









Our hops – Your beer A shared passion
The BARTH-HAAS GROUP is the world's largest supplier of hop products and services. The BARTH-HAAS GROUP operates in all continents, providing support to its customers and partners along the whole value chain: from breeding and growing through processing and to the marketing of hops and hop products. Research and development in the field of hops and beyond are also a key activity of the BARTH-HAAS GROUP. Because your beer is our passion!


 





 





